@liuzhuohua Hi! The app does not work at all on my smartphone for some reason, so can't check it. Is it related to filters or other modules?
First, please check it only with the filters and disable other modules. If you still have it, disable them one by one to find a problematic one.
Also check whether HTTPS filtering is enabled or not. If so, disable it for the app in the app settings.
